我们用一小时二十分钟抵达繁华县城。啃着肯德基，感受挑战极限的成就感。回程一路狂飙，仅用三十分钟便重返校园。青春的旋律在心中激荡，久久未能平复，这便是一次骑行的记录。\n'),(152,53,'post_words_count','1262'),(153,53,'_edit_lock','1744164806:1'),(156,53,'_edit_last','1'),(159,53,'title_style',''),(160,53,'license',''),(165,53,'views','395'),(168,53,'ai_summon_excerpt','清明成都行，是卧铺与硬座的奔波，是“丐”酒店旁的惊喜火锅与川剧变脸。穿梭宽窄巷子古今交织的流光，挤人海看慵懒熊猫的憨态，也静心感受武侯祠的厚重与杜甫草堂的慨叹。繁华，古韵，惊喜，失落……这场短暂的蜀地梦境，醒来后，余味何如？'),(197,62,'post_words_count','385'),(198,62,'_edit_lock','1744252350:1'),(199,62,'ai_summon_excerpt','从`mail-server`的失败到拥抱`maddy-mail`，搭建个人邮件服务器的旅程并非一帆风顺。踩过DNS配置的坑、解决了IMAP连接难题后，我终于能愉快地收发邮件了！分享我的`maddy-mail`实战记录，或许能帮你少走弯路。'),(200,63,'_wp_attached_file','2025/04/1744251933-image.png'),(201,63,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:6:{s:5:\"width\";i:1256;s:6:\"height\";i:313;s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"2025/04/1744251933-image.png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:31639;s:5:\"sizes\";a:5:{s:6:\"medium\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"1744251933-image-300x75.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:75;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:6044;}s:5:\"large\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"1744251933-image-1024x255.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:255;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:31246;}s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"1744251933-image-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:2126;}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"1744251933-image-768x191.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:191;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:21641;}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:5:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"1744251933-image-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";s:8:\"filesize\";i:2126;}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shut